menu "ESP32 USB Audio Configuration"

    config DEFAULT_VOLUME_FACTOR_INT
        int "Default volume factor (1-100, represents 0.01-1.0)"
        default 10
        range 1 100
        help
            Default volume scaling factor for audio output as integer.
            100 = 1.0 (0dB, full volume), 10 = 0.1 (-20dB), 1 = 0.01 (-40dB).
            This prevents clipping and sets the initial volume level.

endmenu